known_issues: Date of Birth field does not populate from quick text/Quick Fill functionality

existing_features.title: Fix the parseStructuredText function to correctly extract and populate the Date of Birth field when using Quick Fill from structured text input. The parser must recognize date of birth labels (including 'DOB', 'Date of Birth', 'Birth Date', 'Birthday') and correctly parse dates in ISO (YYYY-MM-DD), US (MM/DD/YYYY), and EU (DD/MM/YYYY) formats.

projectName: Fix Date of Birth field population from Quick Fill text
